#. module: campus_portal
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_portal.portal_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-eye-slash text-dark me-2\"/> <strong>Horizontal Data "
"Isolation (Data Leakage Prevention):</strong> Absolute <em>Domain "
"Filtering</em> is injected at the <em>ORM Query</em> level. Student A cannot"
" perform <em>URL Spoofing</em> (e.g., changing the ID in the URL from /krs/1"
" to /krs/2) to view Student B's data. Odoo automatically returns an *Error "
"403 Forbidden* if the document ownership (Partner ID) does not intersect "
"with the current logged-in session."
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-eye-slash text-dark me-2\"/> <strong>Isolasi Data Horizontal "
"(Data Leakage Prevention):</strong> <em>Domain Filtering</em> absolut "
"diinjeksikan pada level <em>ORM Query</em>. Mahasiswa A tidak dapat melakukan"
" <em>URL Spoofing</em> (misal: mengubah ID pada URL dari /krs/1"
" menjadi /krs/2) untuk melihat data Mahasiswa B. Odoo secara otomatis mengembalikan *Error "
"403 Forbidden* jika kepemilikan dokumen (Partner ID) tidak beririsan "
"dengan sesi login saat ini."

