#. module: campus_portal
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_portal.portal_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-shield text-danger me-2\"/> <strong>Encrypted Sessions "
"&amp; Authorization Middleware:</strong> Every URL route (Controller) in "
"this module is fortified by the <code>@http.route(auth='user')</code> "
"decorator. Odoo's <em>Middleware</em> layer redirects anonymous traffic "
"trying to bypass screens and neutralizes *Cross-Site Request Forgery* (CSRF)"
" threats."
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-shield text-danger me-2\"/> <strong>Sesi Terenkripsi "
"&amp; Middleware Otorisasi:</strong> Setiap rute URL (Controller) pada "
"modul ini dibentengi oleh dekorator <code>@http.route(auth='user')</code>. "
"Lapisan <em>Middleware</em> Odoo mengalihkan lalu lintas anonim yang "
"mencoba memotong layar dan menetralkan ancaman *Cross-Site Request Forgery* (CSRF)."

