#. module: campus_portal
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_portal.portal_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"An architectural extension that acts as a Frontend bridge between the Core "
"ERP system and the Student as an End-User. Built on Odoo web controllers, "
"this module prioritizes a smooth User Experience (UX) while maintaining "
"real-time data integrity to and from the main database."
msgstr ""
"Ekstensi arsitektural yang bertindak sebagai jembatan Frontend antara sistem ERP "
"Core dan Mahasiswa sebagai End-User. Dibangun di atas web controller Odoo, "
"modul ini mengutamakan User Experience (UX) yang mulus sekaligus menjaga "
"integritas data real-time dari dan ke database utama."

