#. module: campus_portal
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_portal.portal_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"Students log in and are redirected to the <code>/my/home</code> route "
"(Portal My Account) by default. This interface is ergonomically designed to "
"display main metric aggregations, such as current running KRS and grade "
"transcripts."
msgstr ""
"Mahasiswa login dan diarahkan ke rute <code>/my/home</code> "
"(Portal My Account) secara default. Antarmuka ini dirancang secara ergonomis untuk "
"menampilkan agregasi metrik utama, seperti KRS yang sedang berjalan dan "
"transkrip nilai."

