#. module: campus_portal
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_portal.portal_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"Through the KHS menu, students monitor grade movements in real-time. The "
"<em>Single Source of Truth</em> principle ensures that the second a Lecturer"
" publishes grades in the backend, the grades propagate and display on the "
"student portal screen, minimizing information latency."
msgstr ""
"Melalui menu KHS, mahasiswa memantau pergerakan nilai secara real-time. Prinsip "
"<em>Single Source of Truth</em> memastikan bahwa saat Dosen"
" mempublikasikan nilai di backend, nilai tersebut merambat dan tampil di "
"layar portal mahasiswa, meminimalkan latensi informasi."

