#. module: campus_portal
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:campus_portal.portal_homepage_docs
msgid ""
"When a student opens a Draft KRS document, the bottom table dynamically "
"renders all currently offered class schedules (*Available Schedules*). The "
"student interacts via *Point-and-Click* (clicking the "
"<strong>\"Take\"</strong> button) on the desired class. The HTTP request is "
"sent via the <em>Web Controller</em> to the <em>Odoo Backend</em> to bind "
"the data immediately without manual typing. If SKS limits are exceeded, the "
"portal UI blocks it immediately with a *Flash Message*."
msgstr ""
"Saat mahasiswa membuka dokumen Draft KRS, tabel bawah secara dinamis "
"merender semua jadwal kelas yang ditawarkan saat ini (*Jadwal Tersedia*). "
"Mahasiswa berinteraksi melalui *Point-and-Click* (mengklik tombol "
"<strong>\"Ambil\"</strong>) pada kelas yang diinginkan. Request HTTP "
"dikirim melalui <em>Web Controller</em> ke <em>Odoo Backend</em> untuk mengikat "
"data secara langsung tanpa pengetikan manual. Jika batas SKS terlampaui, "
"UI portal akan langsung memblokirnya dengan *Flash Message*."

